WEBVTT

00:01.280 --> 00:04.628
<i>All: # We are the Crystal Gems #</i>

00:04.729 --> 00:07.250
<i>♪ we'll always save the day ♪</i>

00:07.311 --> 00:09.383
<i>Steven: # and if you think we can't #</i>

00:09.385 --> 00:12.252
<i>All: # we'll always find a way #</i>

00:12.254 --> 00:16.155
<i>- # that's why the people #
- # of this world #</i>

00:16.158 --> 00:18.525
<i>- Garnet: # believe in... #
- # Garnet #</i>

00:18.527 --> 00:21.328
<i>- # Amethyst #
- # and Pearl #</i>

00:21.330 --> 00:22.997
<i>♪ And Steven! ♪</i>

00:23.161 --> 00:24.822
<b> 1x20 - "Coach Steven"</b>

00:24.916 --> 00:27.393
<i> sync & correction by f1nc0
~ addic7ed.com ~</i>

00:27.504 --> 00:28.583
[whirring]

00:28.737 --> 00:32.357
Steven: Whoa! What magical
place of mysteries is this?

00:32.441 --> 00:35.026
- Amethyst: Well ...
- Pearl: Oh, I'm so glad you asked.

00:35.110 --> 00:37.777
This was once a communication
hub for gem kind.

00:37.778 --> 00:40.761
But lately, it's
begun transmitting bursts

00:40.796 --> 00:44.002
- of electromagnetic interference.
- Steven: What's that mean?

00:44.036 --> 00:47.288
- Garnet: It's hurting television.
- Steven: No!

00:47.373 --> 00:50.925
I'll save you, television!
Hyah! [grunting]

00:51.010 --> 00:53.740
Amethyst: Sorry, but we
need a Steven at least

00:53.741 --> 00:55.947
[deep voice] this strong for this job.

00:56.048 --> 01:01.797
Steven: [gasps] It's all
the me I could be! [grunting]

01:02.304 --> 01:04.277
Pearl: Amethyst, we
could be here all day

01:04.278 --> 01:06.391
taking out each of these
pillars individually.

01:06.442 --> 01:09.360
Amethyst: [normal voice] Ugh,
I hate it when you're right.

01:09.395 --> 01:11.216
You get this look on your face.

01:11.217 --> 01:13.948
- Yeah, that's the one.
- Pearl: What we need is a

01:14.066 --> 01:18.102
- well-thought-out plan.
- Garnet: No. What we need is Sugilite.

01:18.170 --> 01:22.657
- Amethyst, fuse with me.
- Both: What?! [squeals]

01:22.741 --> 01:23.859
[laughs]

01:23.860 --> 01:27.212
Yeah! Let's mash it up!

01:27.279 --> 01:32.750
- Bigger! Badder! Better! [laughing maniacally]
- Steven: Hold your horses!

01:32.835 --> 01:37.422
- Are you guys going to become a gem fusion?
- Amethyst: Ahh!

01:37.489 --> 01:40.702
- Both: Ahhhhhhh!
- Pearl: Wait!

01:40.703 --> 01:42.844
[sighs]
Garnet, think about this.

01:42.928 --> 01:47.065
You and Amethyst can be a little
[chuckles] unstable when your

01:47.132 --> 01:51.336
personalities combine. We need to
be careful. Fuse with me instead.

01:51.437 --> 01:55.773
Garnet: We don't need to be careful.
We just need to be huge.

01:55.858 --> 02:02.780
- Amethyst: Oh, yeah! Let's wreck this joint!
- Garnet: Synchronize.

02:02.831 --> 02:06.583
[dance music plays]

02:06.618 --> 02:09.616
Steven: What ... what ...
Pearl, come on. I want to see.

02:09.651 --> 02:12.206
[music continues]

02:30.142 --> 02:34.145
[laughs] I forgot how
great it feels to be me.

02:34.280 --> 02:37.594
- Steven: That's Sugilite?
- You got it, baby.

02:37.673 --> 02:41.953
- Hey, Steven, want to see something cool?
- Steven: Yeah!

02:45.407 --> 02:46.595
[gasps]

02:46.596 --> 02:50.161
- You like that, little man?
- Steven: Are you gonna smash

02:50.212 --> 02:52.880
- stuff with your wrecking-ball thingy?
- That's the plan.

02:52.965 --> 02:55.172
- Where should I start?
- Steven: Do that one!

02:57.160 --> 03:01.839
- Pearl: Steven, I think we should go.
- Steven: No way! This is awesome!

03:01.974 --> 03:04.759
- Pearl: Watch it! [grunts]
- Steven: Aah!

03:04.843 --> 03:08.146
Pearl: Steven! Ugh!
You're just too much!

03:08.147 --> 03:10.348
Maybe you're just too little!

03:10.432 --> 03:15.069
- Pearl: Steven, we're going.
- Steven: What?! I'm fine! What about Sugilite?

03:15.154 --> 03:18.940
- Pearl: She can find her own way home.
- Steven: Aw.

03:21.410 --> 03:25.697
- [door chimes] 'Sup?
- Whoa, Steven!

03:25.764 --> 03:29.301
- What happened to you?
- Steven: Oh, just a little battle damage

03:29.300 --> 03:31.414
- from our last mission.
- Really?

03:31.449 --> 03:34.045
- Like what?
- Steven: I got hit by a rock!

03:35.563 --> 03:40.286
[both laugh]
It must not have been a very big rock.

03:40.321 --> 03:44.215
Steven: Well, there's...
internal bleeding.

03:44.299 --> 03:46.455
My hurt is on the inside!

03:46.456 --> 03:49.387
- Oh, okay.
- Toughen up, Steven.

03:49.438 --> 03:55.357
- Steven: You're right. I'm soft.
- If I weren't so modest, I'd whip out my

03:55.392 --> 04:01.106
sweet six-pack and show you
what [straining] a real man looks like.

04:01.116 --> 04:03.034
[grunts]

04:05.788 --> 04:07.143
[lid pops]

04:08.060 --> 04:11.209
Yeah, I'm not gonna
say thanks. [chuckles]

04:11.243 --> 04:14.746
Steven: That's it! We all
need a workout. Let's do it.

04:14.797 --> 04:17.515
Let's work out together.
You could beat up Lars, and

04:17.516 --> 04:20.334
you don't have to starve to
death if Sadie divorces you.

04:20.336 --> 04:22.670
- We're not married.
- Steven: And I know just the

04:22.755 --> 04:24.327
guy to help us out.

04:24.328 --> 04:28.130
[snoring]
Steven: Wow, this looks great.

04:28.165 --> 04:29.644
- Wha... what?
- Steven: Hey, dad.

04:29.728 --> 04:33.284
Hey, Steven. You like it? It's the
best I could do on such short notice.

04:33.319 --> 04:36.350
- No kidding.
- Well, I might join you kids,

04:36.435 --> 04:38.768
show you how it's
done. I've been slacking

04:38.769 --> 04:43.191
on my workout routine for a
few weeks ... months ... years.

04:44.184 --> 04:46.244
- [coughing] Decades.
- Steven: Sure.

04:46.278 --> 04:51.135
The more the meatier! Oh!
We'll need sweatbands. [panting]

04:53.252 --> 04:57.755
Hey, Pearl. Come to
check out some buff studs?

04:57.790 --> 04:59.951
Pearl: No.

04:59.952 --> 05:04.750
- Steven, what on Earth are you up to?
- Steven: We're starting a gym.

05:04.785 --> 05:07.799
I'ma get supa-strong!
Like Sugilite!

05:07.933 --> 05:12.985
- Pearl: You know, maybe this isn't a good idea.
- Steven: What? I want to be strong

05:13.020 --> 05:15.973
- so I can be useful to the team.
- Pearl: There are different

05:16.058 --> 05:19.811
- ways of being strong.
- Steven: But I want to be strong in the real way.

05:19.862 --> 05:25.979
- Come on, Pearl. Let's get beefy!
- Pearl: I'd rather not.

05:26.251 --> 05:30.679
[sighs]
[mid-tempo music plays]

05:30.680 --> 05:32.156
Steven.

05:32.241 --> 05:36.828
♪ Why do you have to look up to her? ♪
♪ aside from in a literal sense ♪

05:36.912 --> 05:40.882
♪ don't you know that a power that big ♪

05:40.966 --> 05:43.368
♪ comes with a bigger expense? ♪

05:43.369 --> 05:48.781
♪ and can't you see that
she's out of control and *ovzeal ♪

05:48.816 --> 05:50.808
♪ I'm telling you for your own good ♪

05:50.893 --> 05:53.395
♪ and not because I'm... ♪

05:53.396 --> 05:58.989
♪ I could show you how to be strong ♪
♪ in the real way ♪

05:58.990 --> 06:04.249
♪ and I know that we can be strong ♪
♪ in the real way ♪

06:04.250 --> 06:06.591
♪ and I want to inspire you ♪

06:06.592 --> 06:09.193
♪ I want to be your rock ♪

06:09.328 --> 06:15.071
♪ and when I talk, it
lights a fire in you ♪

06:15.072 --> 06:17.368
[rock music plays]

06:17.419 --> 06:21.038
<i>Steven: Who's ready to get buff?!
I don't want to see your gut!</i>

06:21.106 --> 06:23.107
<i>I want to see your guts!</i>

06:30.716 --> 06:35.937
♪ I can show you how to be strong ♪
♪ in the real way ♪

06:36.021 --> 06:41.776
♪ and I know that we can be strong ♪
♪ in the real way ♪

06:41.860 --> 06:44.254
♪ and I want to inspire you ♪

06:44.255 --> 06:46.979
Pearl: # I want to be your rock #

06:47.014 --> 06:51.897
<i>Both: # and when I talk,
it lights a fire in you #</i>

06:52.635 --> 06:55.072
<i>♪ I want to inspire you ♪</i>

06:55.157 --> 06:57.825
<i>♪ I want to be your rock ♪</i>

06:57.826 --> 07:01.829
<i>♪ and when I talk, it
lights a fire in you ♪</i>

07:01.914 --> 07:04.036
[all grunt]
[all groan]

07:04.037 --> 07:07.446
[panting]
Hey, Steven, maybe, um,

07:07.481 --> 07:11.051
- you could work out a bit, too.
- Steven: Huh? I've been.

07:11.086 --> 07:14.926
We've been working out. You've
just been singing some dumb song.

07:14.977 --> 07:18.646
- But you're doing a great job pumping us up.
- Steven: Thanks, but I need to

07:18.730 --> 07:23.317
get strong, too.
I'm switching to four-wheel drive.

07:23.402 --> 07:25.236
[panting]

07:27.406 --> 07:29.049
[sea gulls squawking]

07:30.050 --> 07:33.978
Steven, come on!
We're ready to get started.

07:34.046 --> 07:39.333
<i>We can't work out without your
mad coaching skills! [groans]</i>

07:39.418 --> 07:42.434
Be there in a sec!

07:42.435 --> 07:45.115
[groans, grunts]

07:45.116 --> 07:46.958
[groaning]

07:47.042 --> 07:49.606
So sore from getting ripped.

07:49.607 --> 07:53.454
Pearl: I don't understand.
Amethyst and Garnet

07:53.508 --> 07:56.292
still aren't back yet.
I tried to warp back to

07:56.293 --> 07:58.603
check on them, but the warp pad is down.

07:58.687 --> 08:00.888
<i>- [thudding] Aah!
- What's that out in the water?</i>

08:00.973 --> 08:02.029
<i>Are you seeing this, too?</i>

08:02.030 --> 08:04.141
- Pearl: Wha...
- Both: Wha...

08:04.192 --> 08:06.177
[gasps]

08:06.178 --> 08:10.147
[groans]
[thudding continues]

08:10.198 --> 08:14.317
- What the hey is that?
- Aah! [grunts]

08:14.318 --> 08:15.218
[all screaming]

08:15.303 --> 08:18.283
- I'm bored!
- Steven: It's Sugilite!

08:18.284 --> 08:22.056
- Pearl: Y-You're back!
- You left me behind.

08:22.091 --> 08:24.078
Pearl: We just thought
you didn't need any help.

08:24.162 --> 08:26.563
Now, why don't you
separate, and we can all

08:26.564 --> 08:29.042
- sit down and relax?
- No!

08:29.077 --> 08:31.168
- Steven: Pearl!
- Pearl: [grunts] Listen to me.

08:31.219 --> 08:34.892
You've been fused for too long.
You're losing yourselves.

08:34.893 --> 08:38.602
I am myself, and I'm
sick of being split up!

08:38.604 --> 08:42.313
So you better get used
to me, baby, and get this

08:42.347 --> 08:45.933
- junk off my beach!
- Steven: Why is she wrecking dad's gym?

08:46.018 --> 08:50.071
- Why is she attacking you?
- Pearl: Steven, get out of here.

08:50.155 --> 08:51.739
Steven: Aah!

08:51.740 --> 08:54.909
[grunts]
I can't move.

08:55.027 --> 09:00.281
- What? You want to fight?
- Pearl: You'll thank me later! [grunts]

09:00.365 --> 09:05.953
- Come on, kid!
- Steven: Dad, no! Pearl!

09:06.038 --> 09:10.007
[both gasp]
You think you're something?

09:10.042 --> 09:15.669
You... [grunts]
ain't... nothing!

09:18.083 --> 09:21.635
- Both: Aah!
- Steven: [grunts] My muscles.

09:21.720 --> 09:27.058
Pearl: Steven! [groans]
I'm sorry, Steven...

09:27.142 --> 09:30.198
Garnet, Amethyst.

09:31.049 --> 09:34.782
I wasn't strong enough to protect you.

09:34.866 --> 09:40.583
- I'm not strong enough to do anything.
- Steven: Come on, Pearl! Don't give up!

09:40.618 --> 09:43.324
- I know you can take her down!
- Pearl: I can't.

09:43.408 --> 09:47.479
Steven: Yes, you can! Come on.
You always know what to do!

09:47.514 --> 09:50.351
You've got to show her
what you showed me ...

09:50.352 --> 09:54.218
that you're strong, Pearl ...
strong in the real way!

09:54.286 --> 09:56.672
[grunts]

09:59.517 --> 10:02.643
- What?! You want some more?!
- Pearl: Anytime!

10:02.728 --> 10:07.442
You're no match for me!
Not even close!

10:10.936 --> 10:15.935
- Steven: Go!
- Get back here!

10:15.936 --> 10:18.676
[laughs] Nice try.

10:18.744 --> 10:20.490
[grunts]

10:20.491 --> 10:23.981
[gasps]
[grunts]

10:24.049 --> 10:29.954
Is that all you got? You think
that's enough to beat ... ugh!

10:30.038 --> 10:34.375
- Pearl: Amethyst! Garnet! Are you okay?
- Garnet: [weakly] Yeah.

10:34.459 --> 10:37.294
Sugilite just overworked our bodies.

10:37.295 --> 10:39.646
It's a little painful.

10:39.681 --> 10:43.434
Amethyst: And I've got a monster
headache. [both groaning]

10:43.468 --> 10:46.771
- Pearl: Oh. [chuckles] Whoops.
- Steven: Pearl, you did it!

10:46.838 --> 10:50.775
[panting] Thanks.
You make a good coach.

10:50.842 --> 10:54.812
Pearl [groans] we should
have listened. You were right.

10:54.880 --> 10:58.322
- Yeah. I was right.
- Steven: Go, Pearl!

10:58.323 --> 11:02.440
Pearl: Come on! I feel great!
Who's up for a mission?

11:02.475 --> 11:05.115
Amethyst: How long is
she going to keep this up?

11:05.150 --> 11:07.399
Garnet: We deserve it.
Take it like a gem.

11:07.434 --> 11:11.453
- Uh, what the heck just happened?
- Steven: Drop and give me 20!

